These immensely powerful items are forged using magical components and resources. It will cost 10k to fuse the materials together.
These powerful items are forged using magical components and resources. It will cost 10k to fuse the materials together.

When fighting the most fearsome foes across Amia, you might come across a set of Magical Ore. You can create a powerful melee weapon from it with 50,000 gold in materials. Which weapon would you like to create?
